</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="9" pageNumber="76">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="76">Holotype.</emphasis>
♂, pinned, with genitalia in a separate slide. 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="76">China</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="76">Sichuan</emphasis>
: Anzihe Nature Reserve, 30°N, 1312 m, 15.VII.2016, leg. Ji-Ping Wan, genitalia slide no.: WJP17421. 
